The course covers the major types of contracts, including sales agreements, donations, lease agreements, credit arrangements, financial leasing, payment orders and contracts regarding the provision of services.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The focus of this course is directed to understanding the basic principles and concepts common to contracts of all types arising under the law of obligations.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The teaching purpose of the course is to provide knowledge and skills in order to be able to solve practical cases in the main areas of contract law with particular attention to sales law, lease agreements and services.
